-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installation:
1) Extract fy_investigation_v2.zip to wherever you desire
2) copy the fy_investigation_v2.bsp file to \steam\steamapps\YOURUSERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps\
3) Done!

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Feedback is really appreciated! Please rate, and give feedback in a constructive way! 

If you have nothing better to say than: this is a fail map or anything of that sort, please do not waste me and your own time on this.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

What's new?


The upper level has been completetly remade, there is now 2 houses up there, with 2 windows. A doorway to get out, rocks and trees to give the enviroment a very nice look, together with a waterfall in the middle.

 The 2 Teleporters at each spawn has been removed, the "cave" has no ragdolls anymore nor are there any weapons there, instead boths sides has been replaced with some crates.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
